import cors from 'cors'
import { urlencoded, json } from 'express'

export default (app) => {
    app.disable('x-powered-by')

    app.use(urlencoded({ extended: false }))
    app.use(json())
    app.use(cors())
}

import twin from './twin'
import twinType from './twinType'
import thingType from './thingType'

export default (app) => {
    app.use('/api/twin', twin)
    app.use('/api/twinType', twinType)
    app.use('/api/thingType', thingType)
}

import twin from './routes/twin.routes'
import twinType from './routes/twinType.routes'
import thingType from './routes/thingType.routes'

export default (app) => {
    app.use('/api/twin', twin)
    app.use('/api/twinType', twinType)
    app.use('/api/thingType', thingType)
}

import { Router } from 'express'
import TwinController from '../controllers/twin.controller'
const router = Router()

router.get("/", TwinController.getAll)
router.post("/", TwinController.saveObject)
router.get("/:id", TwinController.getObject)
router.delete("/:id", TwinController.deleteObject)
router.put("/:id", TwinController.updateObject)

export default router

import { Twin } from '../models/twin.model'
import { getController } from './base.controller'

const twinController = getController(Twin)

export default twinController
